commentary: Naeem Islam to Stewart, OUT Stewart runs himself out after threatening to do so already in his brief stay. Came down, missed the flick, hit on the pad, thought of a run and advanced. Big mistake. Too late to turn back, gone! More gaffes from the umpires meanwhile as the third umpire shows the green light on referral before quickly changing back to red. Doug Cowie, the ICC umpires manager, is hopefully not watching this game
